				<td colspan="2"><span>Loot whores suck, but that is a risk you take with pick up LDoN groups.
<br />

<br />
You have your wind up now, so that should help with mezzing, dont forget that OOS or HOS can help a lot too, if you get resists, debuff em real fast then mezz away.
<br />

<br />
But hey, sounds like you were doing a great job otherwise.  a couple nights ago I had a group that was Warrior, Ranger, Druid, Rogue, Bard and we were looking for one more.  Warrior wanted to wait for a shaman or enchanter, but none were LFG, so I grabbed a Paladin and in we went.  Warrior was very doubtful.
<br />
2 successes with time to spare later, with me pulling, hasting, slowing and crowd controlling, I had a bard convert ;o)
<br />

<br />
Nothing beats getting /tells by folks telling you how fantastic you are and how they never knew Bards kicked so much a$.
<br />

<br />

<br />
